<br>
Apart from that...hell, I know I have 225+ mana on my armor...lol..may as well make some use of it.<br>
<br>
Also, you can call the ability anything you want...like &quot;body blow&quot; or something...which is to indiciate it is a slow/attack debuff. Why these debuffs? Well, we all know how these are such strong agro inducers. Attach a small predicatable +hate to the warrior is well overdue. <br>
<br>
Such a basic change, would not make wars overpowered at ALL. It brings warriors more inline with the demands of todays exp groups. And allows warriors to become LESS gear dependant. Today, enraging blow weapons are our crutch. (I have quit playing, so I gave mine back to the guild). But this small triggered +hate would be the kick wars need.<br>
<br>
If they also tuned items to have stats SPECIFIC to classes then warriors would be &quot;WORKING AS INTENDED&quot;.<br>
<br>
eg Helm of the Hero can be handed into a quest npc to be made class specific. Therefore mana can be take off the items and a slight increase in hps can be had (ie for warriors). This would help make itemisation a lot easier on verant as they can tune the rewards far more and therefore keep the blurring between the classes a little less. (allowing wars to keep their hps advantage over the other plate classes)<br>
<br>
<br>
Just some thoughts.<br>
<br>
Cuch <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=111730" target="top">Cuchullan</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
Overlord.</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=xathcarnage>Xath Carnage</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 16<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/29/03 12:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2837.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: &quot;Improved Taunt&quot; War only skill</span><hr size=1> I would really rather just have a permanent x2 hate modifier.  A second taunt to add hate rather than move up the list would be nice too.  Then I wouldn't feel so &quot;dirty&quot; when i succumb to fits of mashing. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=252504" target="top">Xath Carnage</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=zebedi>Zebedi</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://home.earthlink.net/~zebedi/images/smallz.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 38<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/29/03 3:44 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2837.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.earthlink.net/~zebedi/images/Zebface1.jpeg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: &quot;Improved Taunt&quot; War only skill</span><hr size=1> Make it a skill, call it Snarl.<br>
